{"tid":1652691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(無棋啦)政府發聲明譴責暴徒在多區施襲","createTime":"2019-10-13T18:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T18:29:34.000Z","uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39a46e9eb5c70183edd143184cc5b1fcc7734298","tid":1652691,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"政府發聲明譴責暴徒在多區施襲<br />\n2019/10/14 02:02 vable news<br />\n<br />\n政府發聲明強烈譴責蒙面暴徒再次在多區施暴施襲，表示極度憤慨。又指行為對市民安全構成極大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指暴徒明顯針對警務人員進行襲擊，包括割傷警員頸部、圍毆警務人員，向警車及警署投擲多枚汽油彈，對警務人員安全構成嚴重威脅，令人髮指，政府嚴厲譴責。政府又指暴徒在多區破壞政府及港鐵設施，投擲雜物在路軌，不單令車站提早關閉，同時令市民人心惶惶。政府會以最大決心遏止暴力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">港共唔係以為有人想殺狗就會民意逆轉呀話，全城拍手歡呼就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2240b0eb4f759debfa56239dc5eabb927c928265","tid":1652691,"uid":154212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"e722849395026e4dad73d90a24fe5d962b9a541d","tid":1652691,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTcsJXv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTcsJXv.jpg&h=9f7ee17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽晚1900遮打花園嘅集會係合法嘅，跪求大家一定要去<br />\n‼️//依家有2個重量級人馬過黎香港視察(Ted Cruz, Josh David Hawley), 而Donald Trump 亦講過香港示威少左人，暗示香港需要搞一次大型既集會/遊行。‼️<br />\n聽日係展現香港人想美國推人權及民主法案既決心，到時兩位都會在場，班狗無得亂黎，無不反都要出，射盲眼，性侵，被自殺等已經忍無可忍，香港人反抗!//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ec3fa0be5a44c2a5ec36e6757b1bf2c59fcf1c","tid":1652691,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"10.14 一定要到！<br />\n仲有乜藉口喺屋企睇live...<br />\n不反對通知書都有埋，<br />\n美國兩位重量級參議員Ted Cruz and Josh Hawley又喺香港視察<br />\n咁都仲唔出嚟嘅話....... <br />\n老實講，以後只能做中共奴隸，<br />\n唔好再叫自己做香港人，無資格亦無機會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpEOto7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpEOto7.jpg&h=fa4ba38e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2415c0a75b3b4ddc64d89b8d3976fc014c925248","tid":1652691,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"明顯針對警務人員進行襲擊<br />\n<br />\n梗係啦，唔通好似你地同黑社會咁打平民咩"},{"pid":"66016152603bd6a4f129b998a8a5e4745d46db30","tid":1652691,"uid":68799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"聽日堪稱呢個月嚟最重要一日 一定要出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652637</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f149768c432c2d863b1123f0fa4ee425fd0067f9","tid":1652691,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:26:06.000Z","msg":"示威者<br />\n激進示威者<br />\n極端示威者<br />\n暴徒<br />\n激進暴徒<br />\n......."},{"pid":"beae42d7a57f25efe3dc992f970635a76b8ee901","tid":1652691,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"問下沙田街坊對黑衣人有乜睇法<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KqaJ_S8GEoc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKqaJ_S8GEoc&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeNxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=16c02e0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KqaJ_S8GEoc</a>"}]}